&lt;p&gt;All of us know that getting to&nbsp;the airport can be tricky. Therefore we have prepared for you&nbsp;limited&nbsp;special offer for transfer to the closest airports in cooperation with our partner &amp;#8211; Transfer Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are the benefits&nbsp;of the cooperation? Transfer to the airport can be paid by using your Diners Club card activating travel insurance for you and all of&nbsp;your fellow travelers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Transfer Service is offering comfortable transportation services&nbsp;starting 2007.&nbsp;Transfer Service counts with more then 15,000 transfers and more then 45,000 passengers&nbsp;a year among market leaders&nbsp;in Slovakia. Company&amp;#8217;s unique car fleet includes only fully air-conditioned luxury Mercedes-Benz limousines with Wi-Fi connection, iPads, local and foreign newspapers, mineral water and refreshments. Their focus is airport transfers, luxury wedding taxi&nbsp;and long-distance&nbsp;transports of persons. In case of social events, Transfer&nbsp;Service can offer you a limousine rental&nbsp;with driver. Transfer Service is a guarantee of professionalism, security, confidentiality, reliability of every order and the most important &amp;#8211; satisfied customers,&nbsp;bringing them to their&nbsp;destination in a timely and convenient manner&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Using the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.transferservice.sk/orders/add/diners-club&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online order&nbsp;form here&lt;/a&gt;, you can choose between:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#8211; one way or two way transfer&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; pickup addresses for all the travelers&nbsp;(pickup in Bratislava is already included in the overall price)&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; date and time of&nbsp;pickup&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; destination airport&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Special offer for Diners Club card holders for one way&nbsp;transfer is as follows:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#8211; Bratislava&nbsp;&amp;#8211; Bratislava airport only for 18 &euro;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; Bratislava&nbsp;&amp;#8211;&nbsp;Vienna airport only for 54 &euro;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; Bratislava &amp;#8211; Vienna city only for 75 &euro;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; Bratislava &amp;#8211; Budapest only for 175 &euro;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#8211; Bratislava &amp;#8211; Prague only for 267 &euro;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The price is calculated with Mercedes Benz E class for 1 &amp;#8211; 3 passengers. At your disposal is also minivan Mercedes Viano for 4-7 passenger for a special limited price.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conditions:&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This special offer is valid for all transfers&nbsp;as stated above, which can be also&nbsp;found &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.transferservice.sk/orders/add/diners-club&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online&lt;/a&gt;. To receive&nbsp;the discount, payment by Diners Club&nbsp;card&nbsp;via online payment or in the car is required.&lt;/p&gt;

